ly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20takes%20about%2020%25%20longer%20to%20make%20long-distance%20drives%20once%20you%20factor%20in%20stopping%20to%20charge%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20bother%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20most%20surprising%20thing%20is%20that%20it%20makes%20long-distance%20driving%20less%20stressful%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-autopilot-not-responsible-fatal-crash-jury-finds-elon-musk-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eautopilot%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20good%20%E2%80%94%20the%20car%20doesn't%20drive%20itself%2C%20but%20it%20does%20give%20you%20the%20feeling%20of%20being%20a%20driving%20instructor%20and%20watching%20a%20kid%20that's%20really%20good%20at%20driving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20other%20cars%20I've%20owned%2C%20after%20driving%20three%20to%20four%20hours%20by%20myself%20on%20the%20highway%2C%20I'd%20start%20to%20get%20fatigued%2C%20but%20with%20the%20Tesla%2C%20I've%20done%2012-hour%20days%20by%20myself%20and%20felt%20fine.%20It%20doesn't%20drive%20me%20to%20a%20restaurant%20without%20me%20paying%20attention%2C%20but%20it%20does%20decrease%20the%20cognitive%20load%20of%20driving%20on%20the%20highway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20was%20also%20surprised%20by%20how%20little%20the%20charging%20network%20matters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20go%20months%20at%20a%20time%20without%20ever%20using%20a%20third-party%20charger%20because%20I%20charge%20at%20home%2C%20and%20I%20know%20where%20the%20Tesla%20charging%20stations%20are%20near%20me.%20I've%20only%20used%20a%20non-Tesla%20station%20about%20six%20times%20successfully%20because%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F04%2F12%2Famerica-ev-chargers-keep-breaking-heres-why-00089181%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethey're%20not%20reliable%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharging%20does%20make%20your%20neighborhood%20gas%20station%20completely%20irrelevant%2C%20which%20is%20a%20positive%20for%20me.%20Most%20people%20go%20to%20their%20neighborhood%20gas%20station%20once%20a%20week%2C%20but%20with%20an%20electric%20car%20you'll%20never%20have%20to%20do%20that%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20of%20the%20time%20I've%20owned%20the%20car%2C%20I've%20lived%20in%20apartments.%20When%20I%20moved%20to%20Seattle%2C%20I%20looked%20at%20several%20apartments%20that%20didn't%20have%20chargers%2C%20but%20when%20I%20told%20them%20I%20had%20an%20electric%20car%2C%20a%20few%20landlords%20were%20willing%20to%20install%20one%20because%20they%20knew%20it%20would%20be%20in%20high%20demand%20for%20other%20tenants%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20think%20if%20you%20don't%20own%20a%20house%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20charge%2C%20but%20I%20lived%20in%20places%20where%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20garage%20and%20was%20able%20to%20figure%20it%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20downside%20I've%20found%20to%20owning%20a%20Tesla%20is%20that%20people%20occasionally%20want%20to%20talk%20to%20you%20about%20the%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-scandal-controversy-leadership-tesla-spacex-ceo-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%20controversy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20thing%20to%20consider%20is%20electricity%20costs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20interesting%20moving%20from%20the%20San%20Francisco%20area%2C%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvoiceofsandiego.org%2F2023%2F08%2F29%2Fsan-diegos-eye-popping-electricity-rates-get-national-notoriety%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelectricity%20is%20ludicrously%20expensive%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20up%20to%2055%20cents%20per%20kilowatt-hour%20%E2%80%94%20to%20Seattle%2C%20which%20has%20cheap%20electricity%20by%20coastal%20standards%2C%20averaging%20just%20about%2012%20cents%20per%20kilowatt-hour%20for%20me.%20Moving%20increased%20how%20much%20I%20was%20saving%20by%20not%20buying%20gas%2C%20but%20my%20costs%20are%20back%20up