rends-are-over-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Girlboss%2C%20girl%20dinner%2C%20and%20girl%20math%20trends%20are%20all%20a%20bit%20much%20to%20some.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhart%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Hart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgirl-math-girl-dinner-similar-girl-trends-are-over-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mohan%20Bhagwat%20May%20Quote%20Ambedkar%2C%20But%20RSS%20Is%20Polar%20Opposite%20of%20His%20Ideology%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F14124741%2FIMG_1874-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ideologies%20of%20the%20RSS%20and%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20can%20be%20called%20two%20opposite%20poles%20of%20the%20Indian%20political%20spectrum.%20While%20Ambedkar%20stood%20for%20the%20annihilation%20of%20caste%2C%20struggled%20for%20democratic%20values%20and%20marched%20towards%20social%20justice%2C%20the%20RSS%20stands%20for%20the%20status%20quo%20and%20the%20revival%20of%20the%20hierarchical%20value%20system%20of%20pre-modern%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20ironic%20that%20despite%20these%20core%20contradictions%2C%20RSS%20ideologues%20try%20to%20make%20a%20show%20of%20paying%20respect%20to%20Ambedkar%20in%20various%20forums%2C%20including%20celebrating%20his%20birth%20anniversary.%20So%20in%20a%20way%2C%20it%20was%20not%20surprising%20when%20RSS%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20in%20his%20annual%20Vijyadashami%20speech%20on%20October%2024%20called%20upon%20his%20followers%20to%20read%20speeches%20of%20Ambedkar%2C%20particularly%20the%20last%20two%20speeches%20delivered%20by%20him%20in%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly.%20Bhagawat%20went%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20putting%20Ambedkar%20in%20the%20same%20category%20as%20RSS%20founder%20and%20first%20%3Cem%3Esarsanghchalak%3C%2Fem%3E%20(chief)%20K.B.%20Hedgewar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUsually%2C%20the%20response%20of%20RSS%20types%20to%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20quest%20for%20equality%20has%20been%20to%20oppose%20his%20efforts%20at%20an%20ideological%20level%20under%20the%20garb%20of%20%E2%80%98our%20glorious%20past%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20such%2C%20the%20struggle%20for%20social%20justice%20which%20initially%20came%20up%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Non-Brahmin%20Movement%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20Nagpur%20area%20of%20Vidarbha%20was%20one%20of%20the%20major%20reasons%20for%20the%20landlord-Brahmin%20alliance%20of%20this%20region%20to%20form%20RSS.%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20this%20alliance%20is%20called%20Shetji-Bhatji.%20The%20Dalit%20awakening%20began%20with%20Jyotirao%20Phule%20who%20struggled%20to%20open%20schools%20for%20oppressed%20castes.%20It%20was%20backed%20up%20and%20enhanced%20by%20Ambedkar%20starting%20the%20newspaper%20%3Ci%3EMooknayak%3C%2Fi%3E%20in%201920%20and%20the%20Bahujan%20Hitkarini%20Sabha%20in%201923.%20These%20might%20have%20added%20tremendously%20to%20the%20awakening.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20his%20pursuit%20of%20social%20justice%20Ambedkar%20organised%20the%20Chavdar%20Tale%20Satyagraha%20(access%20to%20public%20drinking%20water%20for%20Dalits)%20in%201927%20and%20the%20Kalaram%20Temple%20entry%20movement%20in%201930.%20The%20RSS%20itself%20is%20never%20known%20to%20have%20come%20forward%20to%20support%20these%20movements%20of%20Babasaheb.%20Among%20upper%20caste%20leaders%2C%20it%20was%20only%20Gandhi%20who%20took%20up%20the%20issue%20of%20caste%20most%20seriously%20and%20devoted%20time%20to%20improving%20the%20plight%20of%20Dalits%20in%20the%20years%20after%20the%20Poona%20Pact%20of%201932.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20RSS%20was%20propagating%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20Hindu%20rashtra.%20V.D.%20Savarkar%20was%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20theory%20of%20the%20two-nation%20theory%2C%20the%20Hindu%20Nation%20and%20the%20Muslim%20Nation.%20This%20Hindu%20nation%20theory%20propagated%20by%20the%20RSS%20came%20under%20severe%20criticism%20from%20Ambedkar%20as%20he%20wrote%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CStrange%20as%20it%20may%20appear%2C%20Mr.%20Savarkar%20and%20Mr.%20Jinnah%2C%20instead%20of%20being%20opposed%20to%20each%20other%20on%20the%20one%20nation%20versus%20two%20nations%20issue%2C%20are%20in%20complete%20agreement%20about%20it.%20Both%20agree%20not%20only%20agree%2C%20but%20insist%20that%20there%20are%20two%20nations%20in%20India%E2%80%94one%20the%20Muslim%20nation%20and%20the%20other%20the%20Hindu%20nation.%E2%80%9D%20%5B%3C%2Fem%3EThoughts%20on%20Pakistan%3Cem%3E%20(1940)%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmbedkar%20was%20totally%20opposed%20to%20the%20concept%20of%20a%20Hindu%20Nation.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20Hindu%20Raj%20does%20become%20a%20fact%2C%20it%20will%2C%20no%20doubt%2C%20be%20the%20greatest%20calamity%20for%20this%20country.%E2%80%A6%20Hindu%20Raj%20must%20be%20prevented%20at%20any%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20in%20%3Ci%3EPakistan%20or%20the%20Partition%20of%20India%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0(1946%2C%20pages%20354-355).%20He%20was%20against%20majoritarianism%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fcover-story%2Fambedkars-warning%2Farticle23595905.ece%5C%22%3Ewhich%20in%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Indian%20context%20meant%20the%20unbridled%20rule%20of%20the%20majority%20community%2C%20the%20Hindus.%20This%20is%20the%20current%20dominant%20ideology%20of%20the%20RSS%20led%20by%20Bhagwat%20as%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20come%20forward%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Fpm-modi-asked-what-is-wrong-with-majoritarianism-its-a-fair-question%2F1811497%2F%5C%22%3Edefend%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20by%20asking%20what%20is%20wrong%20with%20majoritarianism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20presentation%20of%20the%20final%20draft%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20opposition%20came%20its%20mouthpiece%2C%20%3Cem%3EOrganiser%3C%2Fem%3E.%20A%20scathing%20editorial%20in%20the%20November%201949%20edition%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fram_guha%2Fstatus%2F1250751644293193728%3Flang%3Dzh-Hant%5C%22%3Eread%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20worst%20%5Bthing%5D%20about%20the%20new%20Constitution%20of%20Bharat%E2%80%A6is%20that%20there%20is%20nothing%20Bharatiya%20about%20it%E2%80%A6%20%5BT%5Dhere%20is%20no%20trace%20of%20ancient%20Bharatiya%20constitutional%20laws%2C%20institutions%2C%20nomenclature%20and%20phraseology%20in%20it%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindu%20Code%20Bill%20drafted%20by%20Ambedkar%20was%20a%20major%20step%20in%20efforts%20towards%20loosening%20the%20hold%20of%20patriarchy%20and%20striving%20for%20equality%20for%20women.%20The%20orthodox%20forces%20led%20by%20the%20RSS%20frontally%20attacked%20it.%20Ramachandra%20Guha%2C%20the%20eminent%20historian%20of%20modern%20India%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fbhagwat-ambedkar-rss-8997717%2F%5C%22%3Ewrites%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Sangh%20opposed%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Code%20Bill%20that%20sought%20to%20give%20Hindu%20women%20the%20right%20to%20marry%20outside%20their%20caste%2C%20divorce%20their%20husband%2C%20and%20inherit%20property.%20In%201949%2C%20the%20RSS%20organized%20hundreds%20of%20meetings%20and%20protests%20across%20India%20to%20stop%20the%20bill%2C%20where%20sadhus%20and%20sants%20came%20to%20speak.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Constituent%20Assembly%20in%20its%20wisdom%20enunciated%20the%20provisions%20of%20reservation%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%20Through%20word-of-mouth%20propaganda%2C%20these%20provisions%20were%20undermined%20and%20defamed%20by%20right-wing%20leaders%2C%20which%20led%20to%20anti-Dalit%20violence%20in%20Gujarat%20in%201980-1981%20and%20again%20in%201985.%20Similarly%2C%20reservations%20for%20the%20OBCs%2C%20under%20the%20Mandal%20Commission%2C%20were%20indirectly%20opposed%20when%20%3Cem%3Erath%20yatras%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20a%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20were%20jacked%20up%20and%20then%20BJP%20leader%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20stated%20something%20to%20the%20effect%20of%20%E2%80%9CThey%20brought%20Mandal%2C%20so%20we%20brought%20Kamadal.%E2%80%9D%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E%20oversaw%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20masjid%20on%20December%206%2C%20the%20death%20anniversary%20of%20Ambedkar%2C%20a%20tactical%20move%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhow-bjp-overshadows-dates-related-to-ambedkar-and-the-constitution%5C%22%3Eundermine%20the%20importance%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20this%20day%20for%20democratic%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20the%20status%20of%20religious%20minorities%20was%20concerned%2C%20Ambedkar%20wanted%20to%20grant%20full%20protective%20clauses.%20Though%20these%20clauses%20have%20not%20been%20implemented%20in%20full%20at%20any%20time%20in%20Independent%20India%E2%80%99s%20history%2C%20the%20attempt%20to%20implement%20them%20is%20labelled%20as%20%E2%80%98minority%20appeasement%E2%80%99.%20Babasaheb%20was%20for%20implementing%20the%20concept%20of%20Fraternity%3B%20on%20the%20contrary%2C%20the%20politics%20of%20majoritarianism%20has%20spread%20hatred%20against%20minorities%2C%20leading%20to%20violence%20and%20polarisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20concept%20of%20social%20democracy%20was%20an%20inalienable%20part%20of%20democracy%20as%20far%20as%20Ambedkar%20was%20concerned.%20He%20was%20for%20the%20annihilation%20of%20caste.%20RSS%2C%20on%20the%20contrary%2C%20has%20founded%20%E2%80%9CSamajik%20Samrasta%20Manch%E2%80%9D%20(Social%20Harmony%20Forum).%20For%20RSS%2C%20different%20castes%20were%20part%20of%20the%20whole%2C%20giving%20strength%20to%20Hindu%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHere%20lies%20the%20major%20opposition%20between%20the%20ideology%20of%20these%20two%20streams.%20Hindu%20majoritarian%20politics%20attempts%20to%20maintain%20the%20caste%20hierarchy%20in%20newer%20terminologies.%20While%20paying%20lip%20service%20to%20the%20Indian%20constitution%2C%20ideologues%20of%20Hindu%20majoritarianism%20argue%20that%20India%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98civilisational%20state%E2%80%99%20(symbol%20for%20caste%20and%20gender%20hierarchical%20values%20in%20scriptures%20like%20Manusmriti)%20where%20the%20constitution%20should%20be%20secondary!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECleverly%2C%20while%20being%20opposed%20to%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20ideology%2C%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20is%20paying%20lip%20service%20to%20him%20and%20now%20even%20quoting%20him.%20This%20is%20a%20clever%20ploy%20meant%20purely%20for%20electoral%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fram-puniyani%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERam%20Puniyani%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20president%20of%20the%20Centre%20of%20Study%20of%20Society%20and%20Secularism.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699264846000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F14124741%2FIMG_1874-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fmohan-bhagwat-ambedkar-rss-polar-opposite-ideology%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20ironic%20that%20despite%20core%20contradictions%20in%20ideologies%2C%20RSS%20leaders%20make%20a%20show%20of%20paying%20respect%20to%20Ambedkar%20for%20electoral%20gains.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fmohan-bhagwat-ambedkar-rss-polar-opposite-ideology%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blizzards%20kill%208%2C%20leave%201%20missing%20in%20central%20Mongolia%20-%20Xinhua%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699264819000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105009356%2Cimgsize-110034.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fblizzards-kill-8-leave-1-missing-in-centr