ia-news%2Fbyjus-reveals-rs-2-250-crore-loss-amid-deepening-debt-dispute-4546636%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EByju's%20and%20its%20creditors%20are%20locked%20in%20conflict%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20a%20missed%20interest%20payment%20on%20a%20term%20loan%20that%20the%20startup%20had%20taken%20out%20to%20help%20finance%20a%20global%20acquisition%20spree%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20The%20startup%20had%20made%20a%20surprise%20repayment%20proposal%20to%20lenders%20to%20pay%20back%20the%20entire%20%241.2%20billion%20loan%20in%20less%20than%20six%20months%20through%20asset%20sales%2C%20Bloomberg%20News%20reported%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoelis%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20is%20running%20the%20sale%20process%20for%20Epic%2C%20and%20a%20deal%20could%20be%20finalized%20as%20early%20as%20this%20month%2C%20the%20people%20said.%20No%20final%20decision%20has%20been%20made%20on%20the%20deal%20and%20Byju's%20could%20opt%20to%20keep%20the%20assets%20for%20longer%2C%20the%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Byju's%2C%20Moelis%20and%20Joffre%2C%20a%20tech-focused%20buyout%20firm%20started%20by%20Chinese%20dealmakers%2C%20declined%20to%20comment.%20A%20representative%20for%20Duolingo%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EByju's%2C%20whose%20formal%20name%20is%20Think%20%26amp%3B%20Learn%20Pvt%2C%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20shave%20costs%20to%20reduce%20losses%20after%20a%20pandemic-era%20boom%20in%20online%20learning%20fizzled%20out.%20Once%20India's%20most%20valuable%20tech%20startup%2C%20it's%20now%20locked%20in%20a%20legal%20battle%20with%20creditors%20and%20is%20grappling%20with%20regulatory%20scrutiny%20over%20its%20accounts.%20Over%20the%20weekend%2C%20Byju's%20first%20results%20in%20years%20revealed%20that%20losses%20at%20its%20parent%20company%20narrowed%20only%20marginally%20amid%20a%20pandemic-era%20boom%20in%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJoffre's%20founding%20partners%20include%20James%20Lu%2C%20a%20former%20