20does%20not%20accept%20just%20any%20ride%20and%20ensures%20that%20the%20trips%20are%20worth%20his%20time.%20Bill%20stated%20that%20surge%20pricing%20in%20his%20area%20has%20reduced%20and%20this%20has%20%26quot%3Bmade%20him%20decrease%20his%20driving%20hours%26quot%3B.%20The%20man%20used%20to%20work%2040%20hours%20a%20week%2C%20but%20now%20that%20the%20surge%20has%20reduced%2C%20he%20now%20works%2030%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20saying%20no.%20I%20don't%20work%20unless%20we%20have%20a%20surge.%26quot%3B%20Bill%20stated%20that%20he%20and%20other%20drivers%20were%20able%20to%20make%20up%20to%20%2450%20per%20hour%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20when%20some%20of%20the%20drivers%20had%20to%20temporarily%20stop%20driving%20because%20of%20health%20concerns.%20However%2C%20now%2C%20with%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20drivers%2C%20he%20only%20makes%20%2415%20to%20%2420%20per%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Bill%20said%20that%20he%20employs%20several%20strategies%20to%20make%20decent%20money.%20He%20places%20himself%20in%20locations%20like%20airports%20and%20bars%20during%20rush%20hours%20between%2010%3A00%20pm%20to%202%3A30%20am%20on%20Fridays%20and%20Saturdays%20which%20helps%20with%20surge%20pricing.%20He%20told%20the%20outlet%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20a%20plane%20lands%20and%20people%20request%20Ubers%20the%20price%20jumps%20drastically.%20A%2020-minute%20ride%20goes%20from%20%2410%20to%20%2420%20to%20%2440%20and%20sometimes%20%2450.%20The%20driver%20gets%20just%20short%20of%2050%20per%20cent%20so%20a%2035-minute%20ride%20can%20get%20you%20%2430%20to%20%2460.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2070-year-old%20also%20revealed%20that%20he%20avoids%20%26quot%3Bone-way%20rides%26quot%3B.%20Bill%20recalled%20a%20trip%20where%20he%20took%20a%20customer%20to%20a%20remote%20location%2C%20approximately%20two%20hours%20drive%20from%20his%20city.%20Even%20though%20he%20received%20%2427%20for%20the%20journ