le%20for%20any%20medical%20bills%20not%20covered%20by%20insurance%20and%20will%20put%20aside%20%2415%2C000%20annually%20for%20baby%20Roman's%20future%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20also%20ruled%20that%20the%20couple%20will%20have%20joint%20legal%20custody%2C%20while%20Ms%20Alfallah%20will%20have%20primary%20physical%20custody.%20In%20September%2C%20Ms%20Alfallah%2C%2029%2C%20filed%20for%20full%20physical%20custody%20of%20their%20child%2C%20and%20in%20October%2C%20the%20couple%20settled%20on%20custody%2C%20visitation%20schedules%2C%20and%20child%20support.%C2%A0He%20will%20get%20visitation%2C%20and%20they%20will%20work%20together%20to%20make%20plans%20for%20the%20holidays.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fentertainment%2Fal-pacino-83-ordered-pay-30k-month-child-support-29-year-old-girlfriend%5C%22%3EFox%20News%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20child%20support%20amount%20was%20based%20on%20Pacino's%20reported%20base%20annual%20income%20of%20%242.5%20million.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20they%20are%20still%20in%20a%20relationship%20and%20have%20not%20broken%20up.%C2%A0Despite%20the%20two%20of%20them%20still%20dating%2C%20it%20is%20unknown%20why%20Ms%20Alfallah%20chose%20to%20file%20for%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20report%20by%C2%A0TMZ%2C%C2%A0Al%20Pacino%20and%20Noor%20Alfallah%C2%A0were%20first%20romantically%20linked%20in%202022.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20later%20revealed%20that%20they%20had%20been%20dating%20since%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20In%20June%20this%20year%2C%20the%20couple%20welcomed%20their%20baby%20boy%C2%A0Roman%20Pacino.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Pacino%20is%20also%20a%20father%20to%20daughter%20Julie%20Marie%2C%2033%2C%20with%20his%20ex-girlfriend%20and%20acting%20coach%20Jan%20Tarrant.%20He%20is%20also%20father%20to%2022-year-old%20twins%20Anton%20and%20Olivia%20with%20ex-girlfriend%20Beverly%20D'Angelo%2C%20whom%20he%20dated%20from%201997%20to%202003.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAl%20Pacino%2C%C2%A0the%20star%20of%20the%20classic%C2%A0The%20Godfather%C2%A0series%2C%20has%20starred%20in%20iconic%20films%20like%C2%A0Scarface%2C%20Scent%20Of%20A%20Woman%2C%20Heat%2C%20Serpico%2C%20Sea%20of%20Love%2C%20The%20Devil's%20Advocate%2C%20The%20Insider%2C%20...And%20Justice%20for%20All%2C%20Carlito's%20Way%2C%20Donnie%20Brasco%2C%20Ocean's%20Thirteen%2C%20among%20many%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENoor%20Alfallah%20comes%20from%20a%20wealthy%20Kuwaiti-American%20family%20and%20is%20a%20film%20producer%C2%A0as%20per%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hellomagazine.com%2Fbrides%2F494375%2Fal-pacino-noor-alfallahs-relationship%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0Hello!%3C%2Fem%3E%20magazine%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0Meanwhile%2C%20film%20producer%20Noor%20Alfallah%20has%20previously%20dated%20veteran%20singer%20Mick%20Jagger%20and%20billionaire%20Nicolas%20Berggruen.%20At%20the%20age%20of%2022%2C%20she%20was%20spotted%20on%20numerous%20occasions%20with%20a%2074-year-old%20Mick%20and%20announced%20that%20''age%20didn't%20matter%20to%20me.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Al%20Pacino's%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThe%20Godfather%202%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0co-star%20Robert%20De%20Niro%2C%2079%2C%20welcomed%20his%207th%20child%20with%20girlfriend%20Tiffany%20Chen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699261080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Ftestrol8_al-pacino_625x300_16_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fal-pacino-83-ordered-to-pay-29-year-old-girlfriend-30-000-a-month-in-child-support-4549689%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Interestingly%2C%20they%20are%20still%20in%20a%20relationship%20and%20have%20not%20broken%20up.%20Despite%20the%20two%20of%20them%20still%20dating%2C%20it%20is%20unknown%20why%20Ms%20Alfallah%20chose%20to%20file%20for%20custody.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fal-pacino-83-ordered-to-pay-29-year-old-girlfriend-30-000-a-month-in-child-support-4549689%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fal-pacino-83-ordered-to-pay-29-year-old-girlfriend-30-000-a-month-in-child-support-4549689%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fal-pacino-83-ordered-to-pay-29-year-old-girlfriend-30-000-a-month-in-child-support-4549689%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Odd-Even%20In%20Delhi%20From%20Nov%2013-20%2C%20Schools%20Shut%20Except%20For%20Classes%2010%2C%2012%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20odd-even%20rule%20will%20be%20back%20in%20Delhi%20the%20day%20after%20Diwali%20and%20schools%20closures%20has%20been%20extended%20up%20to%20Class%2011%20for%20this%20week%20in%20view%20of%20the%20rising%20pollution%20levels%2C%20State%20Environment%20Minister%20Gopal%20Rai%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20schools%20will%20be%20shut%20across%20the%20national%20capital%20except%20Classes%2010%20and%2012%20till%20November%2010%2C%20the%20minister%20said.%20Currently%2C%20only%20classes%20up%20to%20Class%205%20are%20suspended%20in%20view%20of%20the%20deteriorating%20air%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDelhi%20remains%20wrapped%20in%20a%20thick%20blanket%20of%20toxic%20smog%20for%20nearly%20a%20week%20now%2C%20prompting%20authorities%20to%20stop%20entry%20of%20diesel%20trucks%20and%20ban%20construction%20activities%20in%20the%20city%20under%20Stage-4%20of%20the%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20(GRAP).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ban%20on%20BS3%20petrol%20and%20BS4%20diesel%20vehicles%20will%20also%20continue%2C%20said%20Mr%20Rai%2C%20elaborating%20other%20measures%20taken%20by%20his%20government%2C%20including%20banning%20crackers%20and%20installing%20smog%20guns.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20odd-even%20rule%2C%20which%20has%20been%20the%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20government's%20flagship%20move%20in%20fighting%20pollution%20for%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20will%20now%20be%20back%20for%20a%20week%20on%20November%2013%2C%20the%20day%20after%20Diwali.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20this%20rule%2C%20only%20vehicles%20with%20registration%20numbers%20ending%20with%20an%20odd%20digit%20will%20be%20allowed%20on%20Delhi%20roads%20on%20odd-number%20days%20and%20those%20with%20even%20digits%20will%20be%20allowed%20on%20even-number%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20need%20to%20extend%20the%20odd-even%20rule%20beyond%20November%2020%20will%20reviewed%20later%2C%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20overall%20air%20quality%20index%20(AQI)%20was%20recorded%20at%20488%20this%20morning%20in%20Delhi%2C%20much%20above%20the%20upper%20level%20set%20by%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation.%20Some%20of%20the%20worst-affected%20areas%20included%20RK%20Puram%20(466)%2C%20ITO%20(402)%2C%20Patparganj%20(471)%2C%20and%20New%20Moti%20Bagh%20(488).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20AQI%20hovering%20around%20500%2C%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20air%20that%20people%20are%20breathing%20in%20Delhi%20and%20neighbouring%20cities%20is%20equivalent%20to%20smoking%2025-30%20cigarettes%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699260600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fv4bskl28_delhi-pollution-ani_625x300_23_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fodd-even-rule-in-delhi-from-nov-13-20-schools-to-be-shut-except-for-class-10-12-4549615%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20odd-even%20rule%20will%20be%20back%20in%20Delhi%20after%20Diwali%20and%20schools%20closures%20has%20been%20extended%20up%20to%20Class%2011%20in%20view%20of%20the%20rising%20pollution%20levels.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fodd-even-rule-in-delhi-from-nov-13-20-schools-to-be-shut-except-for-class-10-12-4549615%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fo