arner.%20Born%20and%20brought%20up%20in%20Moreh%2C%20a%20small%20town%20in%20Manipur%20bordering%20Myanmar%2C%20about%20110%20kilometres%20from%20Imphal%2C%20she%20came%20to%20Delhi%20in%202012%20to%20pursue%20higher%20education.%20She%20is%20currently%20pursuing%20an%20MPhil%20degree.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHoinu%20was%20one%20of%20more%20than%202%2C000%20members%20of%20the%20beleaguered%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20that%20staged%20a%20sit-in%20on%20November%203%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%20to%20express%20their%20anguish%20at%20the%20ongoing%20persecution%20they%20are%20facing%20in%20their%20home%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20student%20of%20psychology%2C%20she%20understands%20trauma%20and%20has%20spent%20the%20last%20six%20months%20counselling%20and%20comforting%20her%20fellow%20Kuki-Zos%20in%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20battling%20severe%20anxiety%20and%20depression.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20violence%20first%20broke%20out%20in%20May%2C%20we%2C%20the%20Kuki%20students%20in%20Delhi%20University%2C%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20eat%2C%20sleep%2C%20or%20study.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20focus%20on%20my%20dissertation%20because%20I%20was%20so%20worried%20about%20my%20family%20back%20home.%20One%20student%20even%20tried%20to%20take%20his%20own%20life%20because%20he%20felt%20so%20guilty%20that%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20with%20his%20family%20in%20their%20time%20of%20need.%20I%20also%20feel%20homeless%20and%20uprooted%20because%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20been%20able%20to%20go%20back%20home%20for%20six%20months.%20The%20reason%20being%20that%20the%20road%20back%20home%20leads%20through%20Imphal%20valley%20which%20is%20now%20practically%20off%20limits%20for%20Kukis%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20sadness%20at%20the%20sit-in%20was%20palpable.%20A%20dozen%20people%20stood%20on%20stage%20holding%20posters%20of%20the%20Kuki-Zos%20who%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20violence%20over%20the%20last%20six%20months%2C%20while%20th