20commissioner%20(CIC).%20The%20post%20had%20been%20vacant%20since%20Yashvardhan%20Kumar%20Sinha%20retired%20on%20October%203%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20November%206%2C%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20elevated%20Samariya%2C%20who%20has%20been%20an%20information%20commissioner%20since%20November%207%2C%202020%2C%20as%20the%20chief%20information%20commissioner.%20His%20term%20as%20information%20commissioner%20was%20set%20to%20expire%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20former%20secretary%20at%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Labour%20and%20Employment%20will%20now%20continue%20as%20the%20CIC%20until%20September%2013%2C%202025%2C%20one%20day%20before%20he%20turns%2065.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20terms%20of%20the%20two%20information%20commissioners%20%E2%80%93%20Saroj%20Punhani%20and%20Uday%20Mahurkar%20%E2%80%93%20will%20end%20today.%20On%20Monday%2C%20the%20Central%20Information%20Commission%20will%20have%20a%20strength%20of%20one%20CIC%20and%20two%20information%20commissioners%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20full%20strength%20of%20a%20chief%20and%2010%20information%20commissioners.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fnew-chief-information-commissioner-2-commissioners-likely-to-be-appointed-today%2Farticleshow%2F104993244.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3EReports%20suggest%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Anandi%20Ramalingam%2C%20a%20former%20CMD%20of%20Bharat%20Electronics%20Limited%2C%20and%20V.K.%20Tiwari%2C%20a%201986%20batch%20Indian%20Forest%20Service%2C%20will%20also%20be%20sworn%20in%20as%20information%20commissioners%20by%20President%20Murmu%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20that%20does%20not%20happen%2C%20there%20will%20not%20be%20any%20information%20commissioners%20in%20the%20Central%20Information%20Commissioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2030%2C%20hearing%20a%20petition%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20lamented%20that%20pending%20vacancies%20in%20information%20commissions%20could%20make%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20Act%20%E2%80%98a%20dead%20letter%E2%80%99.%20The%20apex%20court%20had%20asked%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments%20to%20fill%20up%20the%20posts%20of%20information%20commissioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20elevated%20Samariya%20to%20the%20post%20of%20CIC%2C%20it%20is%20yet%20to%20act%20on%20filling%20up%20the%20vacancy%20of%20eight%20information%20commissioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20three-judge%20SC%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20had%20also%20directed%20the%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20to%20collate%20information%20from%20all%20states%20about%20the%20sanctioned%20posts%20of%20information%20commissioners%20in%20state%20information%20commissions%20(SICs)%2C%20how%20many%20such%20posts%20have%20been%20lying%20vacant%20and%20cases%20pending%20in%20each%20SIC.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESenior%20advocate%20Prashant%20Bhushan%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20petitioner%20Anjali%20Bharadwaj%2C%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Frti-act-will-become-dead-letter-supreme-court-directs-states-union-to-fill-vacancies-in-information-commissions-241201%5C%22%3Eapprised%20the%20bench%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20despite%20the%20SC%E2%80%99s%202019%20judgment%2C%20vacancies%20had%20not%20been%20filled%20up%20by%20the%20states%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20piling%20up%20of%20pending%20cases.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERTI%20activist%20Lokesh%20Batra%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcic-applications-no-new-appointments%5C%22%3Erevealed%20in%20August%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20not%20made%20any%20appointments%20in%20eight%20months%20to%20the%20Central%20Information%20Commission%20despite%20receiving%20256%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22pub