20Su%20are%20particularly%20interesting%20because%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F06%2F13%2Famd-reveals-new-ai-chip-to-challenge-nvidias-dominance.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia%20and%20AMD%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20both%20major%20US%20chipmakers%20with%20competing%20products%2C%20including%20in%20the%20artificial%20intelligence%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20and%20AMD%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Insider%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3EAn%20Nvidia%20spokesperson%20confirmed%20the%20familial%20relationship%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F11%2F05%2Ftech%2Fnvidia-amd-ceos-taiwan-intl-hnk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20Saturday%20report%2C%20saying%20Su%20is%20a%20distant%20cousin%20of%20Huang's%20via%20his%20mother's%20side%20of%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202020%2C%20Su%20also%20confirmed%20their%20relationship%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cta.tech%2FResources%2FArticles%2F2020%2FMasters-of-Leadership-Dr-Lisa-Su%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EConsumer%20Technology%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%20webinar%2C%20saying%20they%20are%20%26quot%3Bdistant%20relatives%2C%20so%20some%20complex%20second%20cousin%20type%20of%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20context%2C%20Huang's%20mother%20is%20a%20sister%20to%20Su's%20grandfather%2C%20according%20to%20Jean%20Wu%2C%20a%20former%20Taiwanese%20journalist%20who%20now%20researches%20corporate%20families.%20%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3Egenealogist%20%E2%80%94%20a%20person%20who%20traces%20lines%20of%20family%20descent%20%E2%80%94%20published%20a%20condensed%20family%20tree%20on%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjeanstalk543%2Fphotos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%3C%2Fa%3E%20account%20in%20June.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fjeanstalk543%252Fposts%252Fpfbid02Z7ib721Hs5zV1cg6gmfQfJ3tz1rEARUwTudASYRMRE3HVyDjFa6SGpAcBsPitxqKl%26show_text%3Dtrue%26width%3D500%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22250%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20immediately%20clear%20how%20many%20siblings%20Huang's%20mother%20%E2%80%94%20who%20was%20born%20in%201939%20%E2%80%94%20had%20in%20total%2C%20but%20according%20to%20Wu's%20family%20tree%2C%20she%20was%20the%2012th%20child%20in%20the%20family%20and%2018%20years%20younger%20than%20Su's%20father%2C%20who%20was%20the%20eldest%20sibling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWu%20also%20interviewed%20a%20close%20family%20member%20of%20the%20two%20while%20putting%20together%20the%20family%20tree%2C%20per%20CNN.%20Insider%20was%20unable%20to%20independently%20verify%20the%20details%20of%20the%20family%20tree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHuang%20and%20Su%20migrated%20to%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20US%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20family%20relationship%20and%20their%20close%20age%20gap%2C%20it%20appears%20Huang%20and%20Su%20did%20not%20grow%20up%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Taipei%20in%201963%2C%20Huang%20spent%20a%20part%20of%20his%20childhood%20in%20Taiwan%20and%20Thailand.%20In%201973%2C%20Huang's%20parents%20sent%20the%20kids%20to%20relatives%20in%20the%20US%20owing%20to%20the%20social%20unrest%20in%20the%20Southeast%20Asian%20country%2C%20before%20relocating%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang's%20aunt%20and%20uncle%20%E2%80%94%20who%20were%20recent%20migrants%20to%20Washington%20state%20at%20the%20time%20%E2%80%94%20sent%20Jensen%20and%20his%20brother%20to%20Oneida%20Baptist%20Institute%20in%20Kentucky.%20He%20attended%