549472%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frashmika-mandannas-deepfake-goes-viral-rajeev-chandrasekhar-posts-digital-rules-4549472%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frashmika-mandannas-deepfake-goes-viral-rajeev-chandrasekhar-posts-digital-rules-4549472%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Many%20Hours%20Do%20Indians%20Work%20Every%20Week%3F%20Report%20Shows%20Interesting%20Data%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWith%20an%20average%20of%2047.7%20working%20hours%20every%20week%2C%20Indians%20are%20seventh%20on%20the%20list%20of%20countries%20that%20work%20the%20most%20globally.%20A%202018%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ilo.org%2Fwcmsp5%2Fgroups%2Fpublic%2F---asia%2F---ro-bangkok%2F---sro-new_delhi%2Fdocuments%2Fpublication%2Fwcms_638305.pdf%C2%A0%C2%A0%5C%22%3EInternational%20Labour%20Organisation%20(ILO)%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20that%20only%20Qatar%2C%20Congo%2C%20Lesotho%2C%20Bhutan%2C%20Gambia%2C%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20have%20higher%20average%20working%20hours%20than%20India.%20The%20ILO%20report%20holds%20significance%2C%20especially%20after%20Infosys%20co-founder%20Narayana%20Murthy's%20pitch%20for%20India%20embracing%20a%2070-hour%20work%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20compared%20with%20the%20ten%20largest%20economies%20globally%2C%20India%20has%20the%20longest%20average%20work%20week.%20The%20ILO%20is%20even%20planning%20a%20special%20India-specific%20report%20on%20working%20hours%20due%20to%20this%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20report%2C%20there%20is%20an%20inverse%20relationship%20between%20prosperity%20and%20weekly%20working%20hours.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20countries%20with%20shorter%20working%20hours%20tend%20to%20have%20higher%20per%20capita%20GDP.%20India%20has%20the%20highest%20weekly%20working%20hours%20among%20the%20top%2010%20economies%20and%20yet%20one%20of%20the%20lowest%20per%20capita%20GDP%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20France%20has%20the%20shortest%20work-week%20among%20top%20economies%20at%2030.1%20hours%20but%20boasts%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20per%20capita%20GDP%20figures%20at%20%2455%2C493%20(Rs%2046%2C16%2C620)%2C%20indicating%20a%20more%20productive%20and%20prosperous%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Narayana%20Murthy%20pointed%20out%20that%20India's%20work%20productivity%20is%20lower%20than%20many%20other%20countries.%20He%20suggested%20that%20India's%20younger%20generation%20adopt%20a%2070-hour%20workweek%2C%20a%20strategy%20used%20by%20post-World%20War%20II%20Germany%20and%20Japan%20to%20boost%20their%20economies.%20Mr%20Murthy's%20remarks%20generated%20a%20range%20of%20responses%2C%20with%20some%20supporting%20his%20idea%20and%20others%20expressing%20disagreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20Narayana%20Murthy%20suggested%20a%2070-hour%20work%20week%2C%20quite%20a%20few%20industrialists%20supported%20his%20idea%2C%20saying%20a%20country%20like%20India%20needed%20its%20people%20to%20work%20more%20than%20what's%20usual.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EJSW%20Chairman%20Sajjan%20Jindal%20said%20that%20given%20India's%20specific%20circumstances%2C%20its%20people%20should%20not%20adopt%20%26quot%3Bshorter%20work%20weeks%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20norm.%20%26quot%3BI%20wholeheartedly%20endorse%20Mr%20Narayana%20Murthy's%20statement.%20It's%20not%20about%20burnout%2C%20it's%20about%20dedication.%20We%20have%20to%20make%20India%20an%20economic%20superpower%20that%20we%20can%20all%20be%20proud%20of%20in%20India%202047%2C%26quot%3B%20Jindal%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20whole%20heartedly%20endorse%20Mr.%20Narayana%20Murthy's%20statement.%20It's%20not%20about%20burnout%2C%20it's%20about%20dedication.%20We%20have%20to%20make%20India%20an%20economic%20superpower%20that%20we%20can%20all%20be%20proud%20of.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FIndia2047%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23India2047%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Sajjan%20Jindal%20(%40sajjanjindal)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsajjanjindal%2Fstatus%2F1717852643928809641%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2027%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESimilarly%2C%20Tech%20Mahindra%20MD%20and%20CEO%20CP%20Gurnani%20said%20that%20Narayana%20Murthy's%20wasn't%20%26quot%3Blimited%20to%20the%20company.%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%9CHave%20been%20reading%20about%20the%20outrage%20to%20Narayana%20Murthy's%2070-hour%20work%20statement%E2%80%A6%20I%20believe%20when%20he%20talks%20of%20work%2C%20it's%20not%20limited%20to%20the%20company%E2%80%A6%20it%20extends%20to%20yourself%20and%20your%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20hasn't%20said%20work%2070%20hours%20for%20the%20company%20%E2%80%93%20work%2040%20hours%20for%20the%20company%20but%20work%2030%20hours%20for%20yourself%E2%80%A6%20Invest%20the%2010%2C000%20hours%20that%20make%20one%20a%20master%20in%20one's%20subject%E2%80%A6burn%20the%20midnight%20oil%20and%20become%20an%20expert%20in%20your%20field%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gurmani%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFormer%20Infosys%20CFO%20Mohandas%20Pai%2C%20on%20whose%20podcast%20Murthy%20made%20the%20suggestion%2C%20also%20backed%20him%20saying%20his%20advice%20was%20for%20youngsters%2C%20especially%20people%20below%20the%20age%20of%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20few%20others%20didn't%20quite%20agree%20to%20the%2070-hour%20work%20week.Shark%20Tank%20India%20judge%20and%20executive%20director%20of%20Emcure%20Pharmaceuticals%20Namita%20Thapar%20questioned%20the%20impact%20of%20long%20working%20hours%20on%20family%20time%20and%20mental%20health.%C2%A0%20'