er%20after%201931%2C%20allowing%20for%20people%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20go%20down%20to%20the%20wire%2C%20on%20what%20each%20of%20the%20numbers%20unveiled%20mean.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWho%20are%20the%20people%20referred%20to%20by%20percentages%20in%20the%20survey%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EToday%20we%20look%20at%20Chaupal%20(748%2C059%20people)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20concept%20of%20a%20caste-based%20society%20has%20led%20to%20two%20sharply%20divided%20sections%20within%20it%20%E2%80%93%20one%20of%20them%20does%20labour%2C%20while%20the%20other%20consumes%20the%20goods%20produced%20through%20that%20labour.%20This%20labour%E2%80%99s%20products%20are%20not%20always%20visible%20in%20the%20physical%20form.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20when%20a%20barber%20works%2C%20his%20labour%20is%20clearly%20visible.%20The%20beauty%20of%20a%20person%20is%20enhanced%20when%20he%20gets%20shaved%20by%20him.%20His%20fingernails%20are%20no%20longer%20dirty%20after%20being%20clipped.%20If%20a%20potter%20makes%20a%20pot%2C%20the%20utensil%20is%20the%20proof%20of%20his%20labour.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20how%20will%20the%20labour%20of%20those%20who%20carry%20someone%E2%80%99s%20palanquin%20be%20seen%3F%20If%20someone%20stands%20guard%20at%20someone%E2%80%99s%20door%20with%20a%20stick%2C%20is%20his%20labour%20tangible%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20346px)%2085vw%2C%20346px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22346%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22495%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20form%20of%20labour%20is%20called%20a%20service%20and%20according%20to%20modern%20economics%2C%20it%20is%20part%20of%20the%20service%20sector.%20But%20modern%20concepts%20do%20not%20work%20in%20the%20case%20of%20castes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20caste%20group%20in%20Bihar%20called%20Chaupal.%20The%20literal%20meaning%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echaupal%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20someone%20who%20sustains%20in%20all%20four%20directions%20or%20ways.%20It%20actually%20means%20someone%20who%20toils%20in%20the%20field%20and%20does%20farming%2C%20is%20a%20craftsman%2C%20is%20a%20protector%20and%20a%20cleaner%20or%20sweeper.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20caste-based%20system%20and%20the%20concept%20of%20patriarchy%20largely%20hinge%20on%20making%20one%20serve%20and%20in%20this%20assumption%20of%20subservience%20and%20service%2C%20Chaupals%20are%20no%20exception.%20Communities%20doing%20labour%20are%20made%20into%20servants.%20This%20means%20that%20if%20someone%20belongs%20to%20an%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20caste%2C%20their%20job%20is%20to%20rule%2C%20thanks%20largely%20to%20his%20access%20to%20resources.%20Governance%20does%20not%20mean%20being%20elected%20as%20an%20MP%20or%20an%20MLA.%20It%20also%20means%20the%20ability%20to%20lead%20a%20quality%20life%20without%20bearing%20any%20hardships.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20a%20scene%20commonly%20witnessed%20in%20villages%20even%20today.%20The%20Brahmin%20priest%20can%20roam%20around%20the%20area%20with%20a%20plate%20in%20his%20hand%20and%20yet%20have%20more%20than%20two%20meals%20a%20day.%20But%20people%20of%20other%20castes%20cannot%20do%20so.%20One%2C%20the%20society%20will%20not%20give%20them%20anything%20but%20will%20only%20hurl%20abuses.%20Second%2C%20the%20labour%20castes%20are%20not%20used%20to%20this%20either.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20people%20of%20Chaupal%20caste%20are%20not%20assigned%20any%20definite%20ancestral%20line%20of%20work.%20They%20have%20been%20doing%20all%20kinds%20of%20labour.%20However%2C%20seldom%20did%20they%20get%20the%20wages%20and%20social%20rights%20that%20they%20have%20deserved.%20The%20concept%20of%20hierarchy%20in%20the%20caste%20system%20meant%20that%20for%20the%20people%20of%20castes%20like%20Kevat%2C%20Mallah%2C%20Nishad%2C%20Bind%2C%20Beldar%20and%20Noniya%2C%20it%20was%20the%20Chaupals%20who%20were%20meant%20to%20be%20the%20traditional%20labourers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20means%20that%20even%20though%20there%20was%20equality%20among%20many%20caste%20groups%20in%20terms%20of%20work%2C%20not%20everyone%20was%20equal%20at%20the%20social%20level.%20They%20are%20not%20equal%20even%20today.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20now%20that%20we%20have%20a%20democracy%2C%20circumstances%20have%20changed%20a%20little.%20Those%20caste%20groups%20which%20were%20earlier%20considered%20ignoble%20now%20play%20an%20important%20role%20in%20elections.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20seems%20to%20have%20Hinduised%20the%20Chaupal%20caste.%20In%20fact%2C%20they%20have%20been%20doing%20it%20not%20only%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Chaupals%2C%20but%20with%20all%20the%20labour%20castes.%20For%20example%2C%20they%20used%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERamayana%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20describe%20Kevat%20and%20Mallah%20castes%20as%20the%20followers%20of%20Hindu%20religion.%20The%20RSS%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20led%20an%20innovative%20experiment%20to%20Brahminise%20the%20Chaupal%20caste.%20Kameshwar%20Chaupal%2C%20a%20person%20from%20the%20caste%20which%20is%20categorised%20as%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%20in%20Bihar%2C%20was%20roped%20in%20to%20lay%20the%20first%20brick%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20may%20ask%20how%20the%20Chaupal%20caste%20came%20to%20be%20included%20in%20the%20category%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20even%20though%20this%20caste%20has%20never%20been%20%E2%80%98untouchable%E2%80%99%20for%20Brahmins.%20Another%20such%20tribe%20is%20Tharu%2C%20which%20has%20a%20population%20of%201%2C92%2C050%20in%20Bihar.%20The%20people%20of%20the%20tribe%20are%20now%20being%20convinced%20that%20they%20have%20traditionally%20been%20equivalent%20to%20the%20Rajput%20caste.%20The%20traditions%20of%20the%20Tharu%20community%20have%20also%20been%20a%20factor%20behind%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20people%20of%20Chaupal%20caste%20never%20called%20themselves%20descendants%20of%20Rajputs%20or%20Brahmins.%20Moreover%2C%20had%20they%20been%20the%20descendants%20of%20Rajput%20or%20Brahmin%20castes%2C%20why%20would%20they%20carry%20palanquins%2C%20stand%20guard%20on%20people%E2%80%99s%20doors%2C%20or%20do%20forced%20labour%20in%20the%20fields%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20Hinduisation%20of%20Chaupal%20caste%20and%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20its%20transformation%20from%20non-Dalit%20to%20Dalit%20has%20been%20done%20not%20without%20reason.%20According%20to%20the%20Caste-Based%20Census%20Report%202022%2C%20the%20population%20of%20this%20caste%20in%20Bihar%20is%20748%2C059.%20Interestingly%2C%20this%20population%20is%20spread%20over%20parts%20of%20north%20and%20east%20Bihar.%20Thus%2C%20the%20arithmetic%20is%20as%20much%20sociological%20as%20it%20is%20political.%20For%20example%2C%20among%20the%20Dalit%20castes%20of%20Bihar%2C%20the%20Dhobi%20caste%20is%20undoubtedly%20present%20in%20the%20entire%20state%2C%20but%20the%20population%20is%201%2C096%2C158%20whereas%20the%20Nutt%20caste%2C%20which%20is%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%2C%20has%20a%20population%20of%20105%2C063.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20are%20the%20figures%20which%20indicate%20why%20the%20Chaupals%2C%20who%20were%20earlier%20not%20considered%20Dalits%20because%20they%20were%20not%20%E2%80%98untouchable%E2%80%99%2C%20were%20categorised%20as%20Dalits.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%20categorising%20the%20people%20of%20this%20caste%20as%20Dalits%2C%20the%20caste%20equation%20has%20been%20changed%20in%20at%20least%20a%20dozen%20assembly%20constituencies%20in%20Bihar%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20no%20candidate%20can%20win%20without%20their%20votes.%20No%20matter%20which%20party%20it%20is%2C%20they%20have%20to%20look%20after%20the%20interests%20of%20this%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20official%20history%20of%20the%20Chaupal%20caste%20and%20its%20people.%20History%2C%20anyway%2C%20belongs%20to%20the%20ruling%20classes.%20The%20subjects%20are%20only%20sporadically%20mentioned%20in%20historical%20accounts.%20British%20ethnologist%20Robert%20Wayne%20Russell%20has%20described%20the%20Chaupal%20as%20a%20large%20non-Aryan%20caste%20of%20Bihar%20and%20the%20United%20Provinces%20(present-day%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttarakhand).%20Regarding%20their%20activities%2C%20another%20British%20ethnographer%2C%20Sir%20Herbert%20Hope%20Risley%2C%20wrote%20that%20apart%20from%20farming%2C%20they%20were%20involved%20in%20soil%20cutting%2C%20fishing%2C%20hunting%20and%20collecting%20indigenous%20herbs%20and%20medicines%20for%20a%20livelihood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Chaupal%20caste%20has%20now%20transformed%20into%20a%20political%20caste%20as%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20political%20scheme.%20The%20RSS%20has%20also%20installed%20Hindu%20deities%20in%20their%20settlements%2C%20leading%20to%20Chaupal%20caste%20members%20getting%20rid%20of%20their%20family%20deities%20and%20perpetuating%20a%20cycle%20of%20subservience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F260208%2Fbihar-caste-survey-what-is-the-history-of-chaupal-caste%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20earlier%20parts%20of%20the%20series%20on%20the%20following%20communities%20by%20clicking%20on%20their%20names%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%5C%22%3EGhasi%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3ESantrash%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3EMadaria%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-koeri-kushwaha%5C%22%3EKoeri%2FKushwaha%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20series%20is%20available%20in%20Hindi%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F260200%2Fbihar-caste-survey-who-are-the-santarash%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20in%20Urdu%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewireurdu.com%2Fauthor%2Fnaval-kishor-kumar%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699256763000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06121548%2FScreenshot-2023-11-06-at-12.15.2.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-chaupal%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20figures%20indicate%20the%20electoral%20compulsions%20that%20have%20led%20to%20the%20Chaupals%2C%20who%20were%20earlier%20not%20considered%20Dalits%20because%20they%20were%20not%20%E2%80%98untouchable%E2%80%99%2C%20being%20now%20considered%20so.%22%2