%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2011-kilometre%20and%20100-metre-wide%20navigable%20canal%20connect%20to%20and%20extend%20Obhur%20Creek%20and%20will%20be%20surrounded%20by%20multiple%20unique%20districts%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenglish.alarabiya.net%2FNews%2Fsaudi-arabia%2F2023%2F08%2F31%2FMARAFY-A-11-km-long-100m-wide-urban-water-canal-that-will-transform-Jeddah%5C%22%3Esaid%20%3Cem%3EAl-Arabiya%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMarafy%20will%20be%20a%20gamechanger%20on%20the%20real%20estate%20development%20sector%2C%20raising%20the%20bar%20of%20development%20in%20the%20region%2C%20boosting%20the%20quality%20of%20life%2C%20and%20creating%20a%20huge%20impact%20in%20Jeddah%2C%26quot%3B%20David%20Grover%2C%20Group%20CEO%20of%20ROSHN%20Group%2C%20said%20in%20a%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20Marafy%20is%20one%20of%20the%20iconic%20projects%20that%20will%20put%20Jeddah%20on%20the%20map%20of%20the%20world%20class%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20waterside%20districts%20of%20the%20canal%20will%20be%20connected%20to%20each%20other%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20Jeddah%20by%20an%20inter-modal%20transport%20system%20with%20water%20taxis%2C%20buses%2C%20and%20subway.%20It%20will%20also%20have%20a%20direct%20link%20to%20the%20King%20Abdulaziz%20International%20Airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20yet%20another%20ambitious%20project%20of%20the%20Kingdom%2C%20which%20is%20also%20building%20Neom%2C%20a%20new%20city%20on%20the%20Red%20Sea%20coast.%20Crown%20Prince%20Mohammed%20bin%20Salman%20(MBS)%20is%20showcasing%20Neom%20as%20a%20city%20that%20would%20overhaul%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20economy%20and%20serve%20as%20a%20testbed%20for%20technology%20that%20could%20revolutionise%20daily%20living%2C%20with%20a%20%24500%20billion%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20intriguing%20features%2C%20such%20as%20flying%20elevators%2C%20an%20urban%20spaceport%2C%20and%20structures%20styled%20like%20a%20double%20helix%2C%20a%20falcon's%20spread%2