0Vinayak%20Goyal%20in%20place%20of%20former%20MLA%20Lachhuram%20Kashyap.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Deepak%20Baij%20had%20defeated%20BJP's%20Lachhuram%20Kashyap%20by%2017%2C770%20votes.%20Mr%20Baij%20got%2062%2C616%20votes%20and%20Mr%20Kashyap%20got%2044%2C846%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20by-election%2C%20Congress'%20Rajman%20Benjamin%20defeated%20BJP's%20Lachhuram%20Kashyap%20by%2017862%20votes.%20Mr%20Benjamin%20got%2062%2C097%20votes%20and%20Mr%20Kashyap%20got%2044%2C235%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDantewada%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBJP%20has%20fielded%20Chaitaram%20Atami%20from%20Dantewada%2C%20while%20sitting%20MLA%20Devati%20Karma's%20son%20Chhaviendra%20Karma%20is%20fighting%20the%20elections%20on%20Congress%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Bhima%20Mandavi%20defeated%20Congress%20candidate%20Devati%20Karma%20by%202%2C172%20votes.%20Mr%20Mandavi%20got%2037%2C990%20votes%20and%20Mr%20Karma%20got%2035%2C818%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBijapur%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%20has%20fielded%20sitting%20MLA%20Vikram%20Mandavi%20from%20Bijapur%2C%20while%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20former%20minister%20Mahesh%20Gagda.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Vikram%20Mandavi%20defeated%20Mahesh%20Gagda%20by%2021%2C584%20votes.%20Mr%20Mandavi%20got%2044%2C011%20votes%20and%20Mr%20Gagda%20got%2022%2C427%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKonta%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBJP%20has%20fielded%20Soyam%20Mukka%20from%20Konta%2C%20while%20Kawasi%20Lakhma%20is%20fighting%20the%20election%20for%20Congress%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Kawasi%20Lakhma%20defeated%20BJP's%20Dhaniram%20Barse%20by%206%2C709%20votes.%20Mr%20Lakhma%20got%2031%2C933%20votes%20and%20Mr%20Barse%20got%2025%2C244%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699254960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F26tj76g_bhupesh-baghel_625x300_22_August_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F