lly%20said%20that%20the%20trend%20of%20governors%20acting%20on%20Bills%20only%20after%20the%20government%20approaches%20the%20court%20must%20stop%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20this%20in%20response%20to%20solicitor%20general%20Tushar%20Mehta%20informing%20the%20bench%20that%20governor%20Purohit%20took%20%E2%80%9Cappropriate%20decisions%E2%80%9D%20on%20some%20Bills%20and%20would%20convey%20the%20details%20by%20Friday%20(November%2010).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20does%20the%20party%20have%20to%20come%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3F%20Governors%20act%20only%20when%20matters%20reach%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20This%20has%20to%20stop.%20You%20come%20to%20Supreme%20Court%20then%20the%20Governor%20starts%20acting.%20This%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20out%20that%20a%20similar%20situation%20had%20occurred%20in%20the%20past%20in%20Telangana%2C%20when%20the%20governor%20acted%20on%20the%20pending%20Bills%20only%20after%20the%20government%20filed%20a%20writ%20petition%20in%20the%20top%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGovernors%20should%20not%20be%20oblivious%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20are%20not%20elected%20authorities%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20CJI%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Punjab%20government%2C%20said%20Bills%20that%20the%20governor%20did%20not%20act%20on%20included%20those%20on%20fiscal%20management%20and%20amendments%20to%20GST%2C%20affecting%20governance.%20To%20this%2C%20the%20CJI%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CLittle%20bit%20of%20soul%20searching%20needed%20from%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Governor.%20Governor%20must%20know%20that%20he%20is%20not%20an%20elected%20representative%E2%80%A6%20He%20can%20withhold%20assent%20and%20send%20it%20back%20once..%20This%20is%20particularly%20on%20money%20bills%20%E2%80%A6%20Why%20should%20parties%20be%20required%20to%20move%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20convening%20the%20House%3F%20%E2%80%A6%20We%20are%20the%20oldest%20democracy%20and%20these%20issues%20must%20be%20sorted%20between%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20the%20Governor.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20also%20comprising%20Justices%20J.B.%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%2C%20agreed%20to%20hear%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fkerala-moves-sc-governor-arif-mohammad-khan-bills-hold-indefinitely%5C%22%3Esimilar%20petitions%3C%2Fa%3E%20filed%20by%20the%20Kerala%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20governments%20also%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699254929000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F21013004%2FIMG_3491.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgovernors-inaction-bills-supreme-court-punjab%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22CJI%20Chandrachud%20made%20this%20oral%20observation%20while%20hearing%20a%20writ%20petition%20filed%20by%20the%20Punjab%20government%20challenging%20the%20inaction%20of%20governor%20Banwarilal%20Purohit%20on%20seven%20Bills.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgovernors-inaction-bills-supreme-court-punjab%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'You%20sneak%20into%20countries'%3A%20Apple%20sacks%20employee%20over%20antisemitic%20Insta%20msg%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699254832000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105003917%2Cimgsize-32338.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-hamas-war-who-is-natasha-dach-and-why-apple-fired-her%2Farticleshow%2F105003865.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105003865.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ENatasha%20Dach's%20post%20was%20widely%20condemned%20by%20social%20media%20users%2C%20who%20tagged%20Apple%20and%20its%20CEO%20Tim%20Cook%2C%20and%20demanded%20action%20against%20her.%20Some%20also%20questioned%20her%20loyalty%20to%20the%20US%20and%20her%20sympathy%20for%20Hamas%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20militant%20group%20that%20is%20designated%20as%20a%20terrorist%20organization%20by%20the%20US%20and%20many%20other%20countries.%20Dach%2C%20who%20worked%20as%20a%20technical%20specialist%20and%20manager%20apprentice%20at%20Apple%2C%20deleted%20her%20Instagram%20and%20LinkedIn%20accounts%20after%20receiving%20backlash%20for%20her%20remarks.%20She%20was%20also%20removed%20from%20Apple's%20official%20employee%20directory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-hamas-war-who-is-natasha-dach-and-why-apple-fired-her%2Farticleshow%2F105003865.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-hamas-war-who-is-natasha-dach-and-why-apple-fired-her%2Famp_articleshow%2F105003865.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-hamas-war-who-is-natasha-dach-and-why-apple-fired-her%2Famp_articleshow%2F105003865.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Volcanic%20Eruption%20Creates%20New%20Island%20Near%20Japan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEruptions%20from%20an%20underwater%20volcano%20have%20created%20a%20new%20island%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Japan.%20The%20islet%20lies%20in%20the%20Ogasawara%20island%20chain%20more%20than%201%2C000%20kilometres%20south%20of%20Tokyo%20in%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EAsahi%20Shimbun%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20quoted%20the%20Maritime%20Self-Defence%20Force's%20air%20base%20on%20Iwoto%20island%2C%20previously%20known%20as%20Iwojima%20Island%2C%20as%20saying%20that%20the%20new%20isle%20emerged%20on%20November%201.%20Iwojima%20was%20the%20site%20of%20a%20major%20battle%20in%20the%20Second%20World%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20personnel%20on%20Iwojima%20heard%20a%20loud%20noise%2C%20saw%20sand%20sent%20high%20in%20the%20air%20as%20the%20new%20island%20as%20created.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Japan%20Meteorological%20Agency%20(JMA)%20said%20it%20has%20detected%20tremors%20on%20Iwoto%20Island%20every%20few%20minutes%20since%20October%2021%2C%20after%20which%20the%20volcanic%20eruptions%20were%20reported%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asahi.com%2Fajw%2Farticles%2F15047737%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EAsahi%20Shimbun%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20island%20was%20formed%20near%20the%20crater%20of%20the%20undersea%20volcano.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20possible%20that%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20rocks%20and%20stones%20ejected%20from%20the%20crater%20on%20the%20seafloor%20accumulated%20and%20created%20the%20islet%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20JMA%20official%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENew%20islands%20have%20emerged%20in%20the%20region%20in%20the%20past%20but%20all%20of%20them%20submerged%20within%20months%20due%20to%20harsh%20sea%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20islet%20is%20the%20first%20in%20the%20region%20since%201986.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVolcanic%20eruptions%20are%20continuing%20and%20officials%20have%20warned%20of%20smoke%20and%20large%20ash%20deposit%20in%20the%20region%20due%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20digital%20mapping%20led%20to%20around%207%2C000%20new%20islands%20being%20discovered%20around%20Japan%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20The%20Guardian.%20The%20islands%20were%20found%20after%20the%20Geospatial%20Information%20Authority%20of%20Japan%20conducted%20a%20survey%20-%20the%20first%20of%20its%20kind%20in%2035%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20had%20no%20impact%20on%20the%20size%20of%20Japan's%20territory%20of%2037%2C000%20square%20kilometres.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699254480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Ft71f0m1o_japan-island-generic_625x300_06_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-island-emerges-from-sea-after-eruptions-from-underwater-volcano-off-the-coast-of-japan-4549423%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22New%20islands%20have%20emerged%20in%20the%20region%20in%20the%20past%20but%20all%20of%20them%20submerged%20within%20months%20due%20to%20harsh%20sea%20conditions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-island-emerges-from-sea-after-eruptions-from-underwater-volcano-off-the-coast-of-japan-4549423%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-island-emerges-from-sea-after-eruptions-from-underwater-volcano-off-the-coast-of-japan-4549423%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-island-emerges-from-sea-after-eruptions-from-underwater-volcano-off-the-coast-of-japan-4549423%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kyle%20discusses%20separation%20from%20Mauricio%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699254306000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105003714%2Cimgsize-30842.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fim-not-thrilled-or-happy-says-kyle-richards-as-she-discusses-separation-from-her-husband-mauricio-umansky%2Farticleshow%2F105003714.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105003714.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKyle%20Richards%20opened%20up%20about%20her%20separation%20from%20her%20husband%2C%20Mauricio%20Umansky.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canon