%22%3A%22Trump%20wants%20to%20use%20the%20DOJ%20to%20probe%20high-profile%20critics%20if%20he%20wins%20a%20second%20term%20in%202024%2C%20report%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654816523cc84b4dfafcbe87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20President%20Donald%20Trump.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FPhelan%20M.%20Ebenhack%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFormer%20President%20Trump%20is%20mapping%20out%20ways%20to%20probe%20high-profile%20critics%20in%20a%20potential%20second%20term%2C%20per%20WaPo.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20reportedly%20wants%20to%20see%20the%20DOJ%20investigate%20Bill%20Barr%2C%20John%20Kelly%2C%20Mark%20Milley%2C%20and%20Ty%20Cobb.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20set%20of%20proposals%20from%20Trump%20allies%20have%20been%20called%C2%A0%26quot%3BProject%202025%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20WaPo.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20his%20associates%20have%20begun%20outlining%20proposals%20for%20utilizing%20the%20federal%20government%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etarget%20some%20of%20the%20ex-president's%20highest-profile%20critics%20should%20he%20secure%20a%20second%20term%20next%20year%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fpolitics%2F2023%2F11%2F05%2Ftrump-revenge-second-term%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Washington%20Post.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20%E2%80%94%20the%20frontrunner%20in%20the%20GOP%20presidential%20primary%20who%20has%20continually%20railed%20against%20his%20loss%20to%20now-President%20Joe%20Biden%20in%20the%202020%20election%20%E2%80%94%20has%20privately%20told%20advisors%20and%20close%20allies%20this%20year%20that%20he'd%20like%20to%20see%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20probe%20individuals%20who%20railed%20against%20his%20first%20adm