rl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ED%20Questions%20Former%20J%26amp%3BK%20Minister%20Lal%20Singh%2C%20Supporters%20Protest%20in%20Jammu%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F05203638%2FFTB-M7zacAExlKZ.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Former%20minister%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20chairman%20Dogra%20Swabhiman%20Sangathan%20Party%20(DSSP)%20Choudhary%20Lal%20Singh%20was%20questioned%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20for%20nearly%2011%20hours%20on%20Saturday%20(November%204)%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20case%20registered%20against%20an%20educational%20trust%20headed%20by%20his%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20questioning%20triggered%20protests%20by%20his%20supporters%20outside%20the%20ED%20office%20in%20Jammu%2C%20who%20alleged%20that%20this%20was%20a%20vindictive%20action%20against%20him%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janta%20Party%20(BJP)%20to%20force%20him%20to%20join%20the%20party%20as%20well%20as%20to%20stop%20him%20from%20contesting%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuestioning%20and%20protests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESingh%20appeared%20before%20the%20ED%20officials%20in%20Jammu%20on%20Saturday%20at%2010%20am%20and%20was%20allowed%20to%20leave%20the%20agency%E2%80%99s%20office%20in%20the%20late%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShouting%20slogans%20%E2%80%9CJai%20Duggar%2C%20Jai%20Dogra%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9CDogra%20Ekta%20Zindabad%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CChoudhary%20Lal%20Singh%20Zindabad%E2%80%9D%2C%20his%20supporters%20gathered%20outside%20the%20ED%20office%20in%20Jammu%20and%20held%20protests%20against%20what%20they%20called%20was%20vindictive%20action%20and%20a%20political%20witch-hunt%20against%20their%20leader.%20Protests%20continued%20throughout%20the%20day%20and%20dispersed%20only%20after%20Lal%20Singh%20was%20allowed%20to%20leave%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20office.%20Singh%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20appear%20again%20before%20ED%20on%20Monday%20(November%206).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20just%20a%20pressure%20tactic%20to%20blackmail%20him%20to%20join%20BJP.%20This%20case%20will%20vanish%20if%20he%20switches%20over%20to%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr.%20Haridutt%20Shishu%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20Lal%20Singh-led%20DSSP%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20questioning%20of%20Singh%20is%20part%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cbrowbeating%20tactics%E2%80%9D%20to%20harass%20candidates%20who%20will%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20party%20in%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20high%20court%20has%20already%20stayed%20the%20re-investigation%20of%20the%20case%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0On%20April%2019%2C%202023%2C%20the%20high%20court%20stayed%20the%20order%20of%20the%20trial%20court%20directing%20re-investigation%20of%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESingh%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20Kanta%20Andotra%2C%20a%20former%20MLA%2C%20said%20that%20BJP%20is%20harassing%20her%20husband%20due%20to%20fear%20of%20their%20defeat%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20are%20they%20harassing%20him%3F%20He%20is%20neither%20chairperson%20nor%20a%20trustee%20of%20the%20RB%20Educational%20Trust%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20mediapersons%20outside%20ED%20office%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20they%20want%20to%20implicate%20him%20in%20a%20false%20case%20to%20stop%20him%20from%20contesting%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20contacted%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20general%20secretary%20(organisations)%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20unit%2C%20Ashok%20Koul%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20party%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20ED%20action%20against%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20the%20ED%20says%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2018%2C%202023%2C%20the%20ED%2C%20in%20an%20official%20handout%2C%20said%20that%20it%20has%20started%20investigation%20in%20the%20case%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20an%20FIR%20and%20subsequent%20chargesheet%20filed%20by%20the%20CBI%20against%20the%20RB%20Educational%20Trust%20at%20Jammu%2C%20Ajay%20Singh%20who%20was%20the%20then%20District%20Collector%20at%20Kathua%20and%20other%20revenue%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20RB%20Educational%20Trust%20is%20headed%20by%20Lal%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20wife%20Kanta%20Andotra%2C%20a%20former%20MLA.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0The%20ED%20claimed%20that%20its%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20the%20Trust%20through%20its%20chairperson%20Kanta%20Andotra%2C%20Lal%20Singh%20and%20other%20trustees%20in%20connivance%20with%20officials%20of%20Revenue%20department%20had%20%E2%80%9Centered%20into%20criminal%20conspiracy%20during%20the%20period%202011%20for%20wrongful%20issuance%20of%20%E2%80%98fards%E2%80%99%20so%20as%20to%20retain%20lands%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20more%20than%20328%20kanals%20in%20favor%20of%20her%20trust%20beyond%20the%20permissible%20limit%20of%20100%20standard%20kanals.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Lal%20Singh%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20former%20minister%20and%20two-time%20MP%2C%20Lal%20Singh%20is%20not%20new%20to%20controversies.%20He%20was%20forced%20to%20resign%20as%20minister%20in%20the%20PDP-BJP%20coalition%20government%20in%20April%202018%20over%20his%20participation%20in%20a%20rally%20in%20support%20of%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20gang%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20an%20eight%20-year%20tribal%20girl%20in%20Kathua%20district%20of%20Jammu.%20He%20quit%20the%20BJP%20in%202019%20and%20launched%20his%20own%20political%20party%2C%20the%20Dogra%20Swabhiman%20Sangathan%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20reading%20down%20of%20the%20Article%20370%20and%20reorganisation%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20he%20has%20become%20a%20vocal%20critic%20of%20BJP%20and%20its%20policies%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20seeking%20special%20constitutional%20safeguards%20for%20Jammuities%20under%20Article%20371%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESingh%20started%20his%20political%20career%20as%20a%20student.%20He%20was%20thrice%20elected%20as%20MLA%20from%20Basholi%20assembly%20segment%20of%20Kathua.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20won%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20from%20Kathua-Udhampur%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%202004%20and%202019%20on%20Congress%20ticket.%20After%20being%20denied%20LS%20ticket%20by%20Congress%20in%202014%2C%20Singh%20joined%20the%20BJP%20ahead%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Assembly%20polls%20in%202014.%20He%20won%20the%202014%20Assembly%20election%20on%20BJP%20ticket%20and%20was%20minister%20in%20PDP-BJP%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EED%E2%80%99s%20questioning%20of%20other%20J%26amp%3BK%20politicians%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20four%20years%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20has%20also%20questioned%20several%20other%20politicians%20and%20their%20relatives%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENational%20Conference%20president%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Farooq%20Abdullah%2C%20who%20is%20also%20head%20of%20the%20Peoples%20Alliance%20for%20Gupkar%20Declaration%20(PAGD)%2C%20has%20been%20questioned%20multiple%20times%20by%20the%20ED%20since%202019%20in%20connection%20with%20misusing%20funds%20of%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20Cricket%20Association%20(JKCA).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPeoples%20Democratic%20Party%20president%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20and%20her%20mother%20Gulshan%20Nazir%20were%20also%20questioned%20by%20the%20ED%20in%202021%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20money%20laundering%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699196910000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F05203638%2FFTB-M7zacAExlKZ.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fformer-minister-lal-singh-enforcement-directorate%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'This%20is%20just%20a%20pressure%20tactic%20to%20blackmail%20him%20to%20join%20BJP.%20This%20case%20will%20vanish%20if%20he%20switches%20over%20to%20BJP%2C'%20Haridutt%20Shishu%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20Lal%20Singh-led%20DSSP%20told%20The%20Wire.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fformer-minister-lal-singh-enforcement-directorate%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Scottish%20first%20minister's%20in-laws%20return%20home%20from%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699195447000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F0E83%2Fproduction%2F_115651730_breaking-promo-976.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-scotland-67326706%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20family%20of%20Scotland's%20first%20minister%20is%20reunited%20after%20his%20wife's%20parents%20spent%20weeks%20trapped%20in%20Gaza.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A230%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-scotland-67326706%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-scotland-67326706.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-scotland-67326706.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Can%20Be%20a%20Good%20Fast%20Bowler%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F05192206%2F3852511928_d9ab80f105_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ETwenty%20years%20ago%2C%20Shoaib%20Akhtar%20became%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.espncricinfo.com%2Fstory%2Fshoaib-akhtar-at-100-mph-126897%5C%22%3Efirst%20person%20recorded%20to%20bowl%20at%20100mph%20(161km%20per%20hour)%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%202003%20One-Day%20International%20Men%E2%80%99s%20World%20Cup%20match%20for%20Pakistan%20against%20England.%20There%20was%20an%20expectation%20afterwards%20that%20this%20feat%20would%20become%20a%20regular%20occurrence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20humans%20have%20continued%20to%20run%20faster%2C%20throw%20further%20and%20jump%20higher%2C%20it%20was%20believed%20that%20this%20milestone%20would%20be%20a%20stepping%20stone%20consigned%20to%20history%20similar%20to%20Roger%20Bannister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guinnessworldrecords.com%2Frecords%2Fhall-of-fame%2Ffirst-sub-four-minute-mile%5C%22%3Ebreaking%20the%20four-minute%20mile%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20thought%20it%20might%20also%20act%20as%20a%20catalyst%20for%20serious%20worldwide%20improvement%20in%20fast%20bowling.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20despite%20continuing%20improvement%20in%20the%20athletic%20ability%20of%20fast%20bowlers%2C%20the%20magical%20three-figure%20barrier%20has%20only%20been%20surpassed%20since%20by%20Brett%20Lee%20and%20Shaun%20Tait%20%E2%80%93%20and%20not%20for%20over%20ten%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHas%20cricket%20fast%20bowling%E2%80%99s%20top%20speed%20stalled%3F%20During%20the%20current%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cricketworldcup.com%2F%5C%22%3E2023%20One-Day%20International%20Men%E2%80%99s%20World%20Cup%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20hosted%20in%20India%2C%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20bowlers%20have%20produced%20speeds%20over%2090mph%20(145km%20per%20hour)%2C%20with%20the%20fastest%20being%20around%2095mph%20(153%20km%20per%20hour).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20performance%20of%20cricket%20fast%20bowlers%20almost%20entirely%20depends%20on%20two%20factors.%20The%20first%20is%20the%20amount%20of%20momentum%20developed%20in%20the%20run-up%20and%20maintained%20before%20the%20front%20foot%20contacting%20the%20floor.%20The%20second%20is%20the%20technique%20employed%20to%20generate%20and%20transfer%20momentum%20within%20the%20body%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FBowling_action%23%2Fmedia%2FFile%3ABowling_action.png%5C%22%3Eduring%20the%20bowling%20phase%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20the%20front%20foot%20contacting%20the%20floor%20and%20the%20release%20of%20the%20ball%20from%20the%20bowler%E2%80%99s%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.humankinetics.com%2Fview%2Fjournals%2Fjab%2F29%2F1%2Farticle-p78.xml%5C%22%3EPrevious%20research%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20highlighted%20that%20the%20fastest%20elite%20male%20bowlers%20generate%20more%20momentum%20in%20their%20run-up%2C%20adopting%20a%20movement%20strategy%20that%20aims%20to%20maintain%20and%20transfer%20this%20momentum%20into%20the%20throw%20instead%20of%20generating%20additional%20momentum%20from%20their%20muscles.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETesting%20the%20limits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20investigate%20the%20limits%20of%20fast%20bowling%20performance%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flinkinghub.elsevier.com%2Fretrieve%2Fpii%2FS0021929023003354%5C%22%3Eworld-leading%20predictive%20musculoskeletal%20computer%20simulation%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20ten%20elite%20male%20fast%20bowlers%20(essentially%20a%20virtual%20clone%20of%20each%20bowler)%20was%20developed.%20It%20then%20optimised%20their%20technique%20to%20maximise%20the%20release%20speed%20of%20the%20ball.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20none%20of%20these%20bowlers%20were%20predicted%20by%20the%20computer%20model%20to%20break%20the%20100mph%20barrier.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20why%20the%20top%20speed%20has%20stalled%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20consider%20how%20all%20the%20factors%20influencing%20human%20movement%20patterns%20affect%20the%20technique%20of%20fast%20bowlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Farticle%2F10.2165%2F00007256-200333040-00001%5C%22%3EThe%20behaviour%20of%20all%20our%20movement%20patterns%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20shaped%20by%20three%20types%20of%20constraint.%20The%20first%20is%20organismic%3A%20these%20are%20constraints%20on%20the%20individual%2C%20such%20as%20their%20size%2C%20strength%20and%20range%20of%20motion.%20The%20second%20factor%20shaping%20movement%20patterns%20is%20the%20environment%20the%20individual%20interacts%20with%2C%20including%20the%20atmosphere%2C%20temperature%2C%20equipment%20and%20surfaces.%20The%20third%20shaping%20factor%20is%20the%20task%2C%20which%20involves%20constraints%20such%20as%20the%20goal%20of%20the%20activity%2C%20the%20rules%20and%20the%20intensity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOur%20previous%20experiences%20of%20the%20movement%20%E2%80%93%20what%20we%20have%20seen%2C%20what%20we%20have%20been%20told%20and%20our%20previous%20performance%20of%20the%20movement%20%E2%80%93%20also%20affect%20individual%20technique%20in%20fast%20bowling.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20innate%20physiology%20of%20the%20fast%20bowler%2C%20an%20organismic%20constraint%2C%20provides%20the%20only%20potential%20area%20for%20development%20in%20fast%20bowling.%20The%20other%20constraints%2C%20such%20as%20environment%20and%20task%2C%20which%20often%20lead%20to%20scientific%20and%20technological%20development%20associated%20with%20improvements%20in%20other%20sports%2C%20are%20extremely%20limited%20in%20fast%20bowling.%20This%20is%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20equipment%20and%20the%20simplicity%20of%20the%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20physiological%20aspect%20often%20considered%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20improvements%20in%20fast%20bowling%20performance%20is%20an%20increase%20in%20muscular%20strength%2C%20power%20and%20endurance.%20However%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20unique%20cricket%20bowling%20%E2%80%9Ctask%E2%80%9D%20constraint%20which%20requires%20bowlers%20to%20maintain%20a%20straight%20arm%20during%20the%20bowling%20phase.%20This%20significantly%20reduces%20the%20time%20available%20to%20complete%20the%20throwing%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExplosive%20activation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EElite%20males%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1080%2F02640414.2018.1522700%5C%22%3Ecomplete%20the%20bowling%20phase%20in%20approximately%20100%20milliseconds%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20is%20similar%20to%20the%20time%20required%20to%20explosively%20activate%20a%20single%20muscle.%20This%20limits%20the%20ability%20of%20bowlers%20to%20develop%20additional%20momentum%20using%20their%20muscles%20in%20the%20bowling%20phase%20and%20neutralises%20the%20effect%20of%20strength%20increases%20on%20ball%20speed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20explains%20why%20maximising%20momentum%20generated%20during%20the%20run-up%20is%20preferred%20over%20generating%20muscular%20momentum%20during%20the%20bowling%20phase.%20It%20also%20explains%20why%20fast%20bowling%20top%20speeds%20have%20not%20increased%20despite%20recent%20advances%20in%20fast%20bowlers%E2%80%99%20athletic%20abilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1080%2F02640414.2018.1522700%5C%22%3Eresearch%20on%20women%20fast%20bowlers%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20highlighted%20that%20bowlers%20who%20generate%20less%20momentum%20during%20the%20run-up%20and%20therefore%20have%20more%20time%20available%20to%20generate%20additional%20muscular%20momentum%2C%20adopt%20a%20movement%20pattern%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.assaf.org.za%2Findex.php%2Fsajsm%2Farticle%2Fview%2F15080%5C%22%3Emore%20akin%20to%20throwing%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20this%20approach%2C%20the%20momentum%20generated%20in%20the%20run-up%20is%20added%20to%20via%20the%20use%20of%20large%20rotational%20torso%20muscles%20within%20the%20bowling%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EImprovements%20to%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20large%20rotational%20torso%20muscles%20in%20men%20and%20women%20could%20possibly%20improve%20the%20generation%20of%20muscular%20momentum.%20But%20this%20approach%20is%20considered%20a%20sub-optimal%20technique%20by%20the%20research%20that%E2%80%99s%20been%20carried%20out%20on%20fast%20bowling.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20potential%20mechanism%20to%20increase%20the%20time%20available%20to%20develop%20more%20momentum%20from%20muscles%20would%20be%20to%20increase%20the%20range%20of%20motion%20that%20joints%20move%20through%20during%20the%20bowling%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJoint%20%E2%80%98hypermobility%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F02640414.2023.2200520%5C%22%3ERecent%20research%20has%20highlighted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2C%20on%20average%2C%20elite%20fast%20bowlers%20with%20an%20increased%20range%20of%20motion%20in%20the%20hip%20and%20shoulder%20had%20greater%20ball%20release%20speeds.%20It%20was%20also%20suggested%20that%20the%20bowlers%E2%80%99%20techniques%20were%20probably%20influenced%20by%20their%20range%20of%20motion%20during%20their%20early%20learning%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20elbow%20hyperextension%20%E2%80%93%20where%20the%20joint%20travels%20beyond%20a%20straight%20position%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1080%2F02640414.2015.1137340%5C%22%3Ehas%20been%20shown%20to%20increase%20the%20speed%20of%20ball%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20up%20to%205%25%20during%20the%20bowling%20phase.%20A%20common%20misconception%2C%20however%2C%20is%20that%20taller%20bowlers%20will%20bowl%20faster%20due%20to%20the%20benefit%20associated%20with%20increased%20limb%20length.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20as%20limbs%20get%20longer%2C%20they%20get%20more%20difficult%20to%20rotate.%20As%20muscular%20strength%20does%20not%20scale%20equally%20with%20limb%20length%20this%20becomes%20a%20disadvantage.%20Thus%2C%20an%20optimal%20height%20for%20fast%20bowlers%20probably%20exists%2C%20though%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOrganismic%20factors%20linked%20with%20increased%20ball%20speed%20such%20as%20body%20shape%2C%20size%20and%20hypermobility%20are%20largely%20genetic.%20Since%20human%20evolution%20is%20extremely%20slow%2C%20advances%20in%20ball%20release%20speed%20are%20likely%20to%20follow%20at%20a%20similar%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20100mph%20barrier%2C%20therefore%2C%20should%20be%20viewed%20more%20as%20a%20mountain%20that%20requires%20a%20once-every-generation%20bowler%20to%20scale%20rather%20than%20a%20dam%20in%20a%20river.%20The%20potential%20of%20this%20peak%20to%20grow%20is%20limited%20by%20the%20constraints%20of%20the%20task%20and%20by%20our%20innate%20physiology.%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F216589%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPaul%20Felton%2C%20Senior%20Lecturer%20in%20Biomechanics%20in%20the%20School%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology%2C%20Nottingham%20Trent%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republished%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%5C%22%3EThe%20Conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20a%20Creative%20Commons%20license.%20Read%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fthe-best-techniques-for-being-a-cricket-fast-bowler-according-to-science-216589%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20article%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699192410000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F05192206%2F3852511928_d9ab80f105_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fwho-can-be-a-good-fast-bowler%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Recent%20research%20has%20highlighted%20that%2C%20on%20average%2C%20elite%20fast%20bowlers%20with%20an%20increased%20range%20of%20motion%20in%20the%20hip%20and%20shoulder%20have%20greater%20ball%20release%20speeds.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fwho-can-be-a-good-fast-bowler%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine%20war%20not%20at%20'stalemate'%2C%20Zelenskyy%20says%22%2C%22content%