ity%20everyday%20in%20January%202023%2C%20which%20was%2040%20percent%20of%20the%20daily%20demand.%20Several%20parts%20of%20the%20state%20face%20daily%20power%20cuts%20from%20anywhere%20between%20four%20to%20almost%20eight%20to%20nine%20hours%20a%20day%20in%20some%20remote%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUday%20soon%20understood%20that%20residents%20of%20villages%20like%20Bichpuri%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20financial%20means%20to%20afford%20appliances%20like%20inverters.%20He%20wanted%20to%20find%20and%20develop%20a%20solution%20for%20rural%20India%E2%80%99s%20power%20crisis.%20After%2024%20prototypes%2C%20thousands%20of%20hours%2C%20and%20eight%20months%2C%20the%2018-year-old%20built%20the%20solution%20%E2%80%93%20an%20inverter%20bulb%20that%20can%20provide%20a%20backup%20of%20almost%2010%20hours%20in%20case%20of%20a%20power%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20make%20a%20bulb%20that%20solves%20the%20problem.%20Speaking%20to%20those%20young%20children%20and%20seeing%20their%20troubles%20really%20moved%20me.%20Reading%20about%20the%20heat%20crisis%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20motivated%20me%20to%20solve%20this%20problem.%20How%20could%20they%20stay%20without%20electricity%20in%20such%20extreme%20weather%20conditions%3F%E2%80%9D%20Uday%20Bhatia%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20solution%20at%20Rs%20250%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20768px)%20100vw%2C%20768px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FUday2-2-1699023289.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Uday%20worked%20on%2024%20prototypes%20over%208%20months%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FUday2-2-1699023289.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FUday2-2-1699023289-225x300.jpe